description: Hop on over to The Doghouse for the tastiest Hot Dogs in T-Town! Come get served up with some wonderful wieners, top ‘em up with top-quality toppings, choose which bun is the one (they even offer King Hawaiian Buns, for the perfect salty & sweet meaty treat), and then you’re ready to run! We have a food truck and several hot dog carts. We do catering of all types and sizes. We also offer more than just hot dogs! With our food truck we can do dogs, tacos, sandwiches, soup, desserts, and much more! We were voted best food truck in Tulsa by UTW two years in a row and just recently voted best hot dogs in Tulsa.
name: Doghouse Tulsa
